  "body": "<p>Love that <a href=\"http://www.fynesdesigns.com/\">Fynes Designs</a> put together a list of <a href=\"http://www.fynesdesigns.com/50-christmas-gift-ideas-for-crafty-women/\">50 Christmas Gift Ideas for Crafty Women</a>. It wasn't all too hard for me to come up with the list of items, as her categories are perfectly suited so you can find the ideal gift in your budget. Here are my picks:</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b1116ee2e5225d93.jpg?v=1782530702\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<ul><li><p>Stocking stuffer- <a href=\"http://bit.ly/IlNJBT\">Kelly Purkey washi tapes</a></p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Big ticket item-<a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/black\"> Silhouette</a> - these machines are a must-have and there are <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/black\">Black Friday specials</a> going on through December 8th - Use code: TANGERINE</p></li><li><p>Something to read or learn- (book, online class, event etc.) <a href=\"http://craftcationconference.com/\">Craftcation Conference - Ventura, CA</a></p></li><li><p>Can’t live without- <a href=\"http://amzn.to/1gfP7kF\">American Crafts This to That adhesive</a></p></li><li><p>Something personal- Choose a print from Kal Barteski's <a href=\"http://kalbarteski.bigcartel.com/\">amazing shop</a></p></li></ul><p>Happy gifting! I would love your suggestions for some small shops/etsy stores for unique items. Is there anything else you crafters can't live without?</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}